snippet.title: Swords & Soldiers: Super Saucy Sausage Fest Trailer
snippet.description: Revisit the 2D battlefields of Swords & Soldiers to experience the epic story of Chief Meat. Take control of the Chief and his troops on their journey to the annual Super Saucy Sausage Fest with a massive and meaty grand prize at the end. You will meet new friends to join your forces along the way, and old enemies who will do everything to keep the Chief from winning the Sausage Fest.
